Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:14.91,Alt,,0,0,0,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Dai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Reina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:35.09,Alt,,0,0,0,,Are you going away somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.10,Alt,,0,0,0,,Nope! We came to visit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.89,Alt,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like sweet buns, Reina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a sweet bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a round and sweet snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, go get Reina-chan some barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Come on, Reina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just having snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever tried one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been here before, but it feels so much like Granddad's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to tell me what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought her school bag and stuff here on a Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that we've run away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll all be worried sick about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is it that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Did something happen with your husb{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with his pare{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess living with your husband's parents must be difficult, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's just impossible for people to live together without tearing each other apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's the same maths textbook we use!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any siblings, so we don't really have anywhere else to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.69,Alt,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if we stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're going to have to tell me a bit more about the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.02,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let me see your other textbooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you told your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.07,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sure! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ah! Your Japanese textbook is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I left a note behind for my husband and his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.74,Alt,,0,0,0,,I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell them where I was going, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll take Reina to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought about much beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I haven't told my parents yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't really thought about much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you brought your daughter here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to get out of that house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear another second there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's go pick up some things for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.44,Alt,,0,0,0,,You're right! It really is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't offer you much, but you can use the room on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. It's a little heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck do you have stuffed in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina's slippers and textbooks are in there, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai-chan, I know what sort of stuff you get by on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so tonight, I'll whip you up a real meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, can we go and look at the sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can have one each.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of meat should we get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That one isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this one's not so good, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Daikichi-san! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai-chan, this ground beef and pork is really cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name's Haruko. She's my cousin on my mother's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she need to know which side I'm on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.84,Alt,,0,0,0,,My son is one of Rin-chan's classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.64,Alt,,0,0,0,,and Daikichi-san is always helping me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. What am I saying? She didn't even ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,I see! Then he'll be the same age as my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know why I'm making excuses, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"You've got it all wrong!"? What the heck was I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.81,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She just started first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.14,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What sweets did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Deluxe Big Nyan Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting vegetable cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting candy with a toy of Meow Meow Tumbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those really sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really pretty, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I guess she's one of the prettier mothers I've met...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go about having a fling with her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you some kind of moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, she has her hands full taking care of Kouki on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't even have time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,On her own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen too many weird dramas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks about two or three years older than us. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I care how old she is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's divorced, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried something a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, my mother-in-law has the last say on everything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, we should have this at home, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reina. Hold your chopsticks properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor's all creaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.32,Alt,,0,0,0,,Reina! Take this towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reina! Don't pull on it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They were both pretty hyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved Rin-chan into your futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been too long since I've had alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Want something to eat, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been putting on weight recently, so I'll give it a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean I've really gained weight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that we're definitely in our thirties now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take just being thirty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get older, you just can't push yourself in the same way, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to start taking care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, it's not like my husband looks at me anymore, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who I'm trying to stay thin for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,While you guys were in the bath, I called your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why?! Don't do weird things like that, Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not weird. They'll be worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All I told them was that you were both okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you'll be staying with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even tell them my address.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I already left them a letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do what you want, but I'm worried about Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina's with me, and she's holding up fine. What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, if you don't tell them where you are and that she's okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,how the heck are they supposed to know she's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to calm down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.81,Alt,,0,0,0,,Do you just want to cause your family trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa and Mama are always fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they're married?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Even though they're married. I always pretend to just be asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Every single day, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the day I got married, I've kept my feelings bottled up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the right to cause them a bit of trouble, don't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Dai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a horrible thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Dai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, are you making breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Rin-chan make you breakfast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We always make meals together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we're cooking with a flame, I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,Play nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've got rice on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up quickly. We're taking the train to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could that be at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kouki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come in, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disturbing the neighbours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, is your school far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to leave this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun's mum is busy, so he comes here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, did you get married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! She's my cousin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, you want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, you'd rather be single, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "single"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It means not being married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I've heard of that! "Divorce", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what "divorce" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... So your mum is married, but she wants to be single...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And Daikichi is single, but wants to be married?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults are so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, can I have a rice ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You had breakfast before you came here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That one was supposed to be mine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good heart, huh, Dai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I gave a kid a rice ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just as busy as her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really have a thing for that pretty mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Id{\fscx300}-{\r} Blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought that I could help out a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rin gets along well with the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure Kouki and his mum have been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be rude of me to not respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Single mothers really have it hard, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:22.03,Alt,,0,0,0,,Reina! I told you to hurry! We're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to keep where we're staying a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina-chan, did you come with your mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We secretly ran away from home, so we came by train today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting you another one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it might be waiting for us when we get home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're working late tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! My husband's watching the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is Yuu-kun well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been so full of beans recently that I've barely been able to handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice that your husband helps out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only because his business trip was rescheduled, so he's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't leave raising a kid to your husband, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Reina-chan's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home, Reina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They fell asleep right away tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko, don't tell me that you're going to take things even further than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean a divorce or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me, getting all worked up for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've thought about it plenty of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think about it pretty much every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, when you start thinking about the man\Nyou're married to as an enemy, things are already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Apart from Reina, they're all strangers and enemies to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of our family being just the two of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but someone in my position simply can't afford to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have Reina to think about, and then there's the question of how I'd make a living...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And with all the battles I'd have to fight to break away from my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I'm better off just sticking with things the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I got married as soon as I joined a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At that age, all I thought about was becoming a good wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else to it. No other way to protect Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not even married,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and just keeping a family going is pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You do everything yourself, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I haven't been able to do anything for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is at all! Rin-chan looks like she's having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When she's cooking for you, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kouki-kun and his mother are doing just fine on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so Reina and I will be okay with just the two of us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep saying it's just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you talk to your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always stuck doing overtime, so we never talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll do my best with just Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've put up with it for so many years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I stop myself from feeling too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let pretty much anything go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really unhealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the contrary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't do it, I'd fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten really strong, Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To raise a kid, you need to be able to\Ncall up these huge surges of strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,especially when she's still a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know what it's like with a baby, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I was doing that, I just sort of ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to end up as some old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to just stay as a girl forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Dai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to become a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn, Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"It really is" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa's coming after he finishes work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be here this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely Papa! I'm not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina, it's not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you, Reina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. So if he {\i1}actually{\i0} wants to get off\Nwork at this time, he has no problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty hard working at a company, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,Stupid Hideyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko's caused you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it really wasn't a...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing the wrong clothes for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Dai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa could at least carry our bags, couldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always so inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! "Inconsridat"!{Done on purpose}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come back any time you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't cause you any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin is always going on about how much she wants to see Reina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Dai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then can we come this Sunday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko as a child, always in tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And Haruko last night, whispering\Nthat she wanted to be a girl forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you come, pack a little lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms hurt just looking at that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls have an awful lot of things to carry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but maybe this one would suit you better...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I try this one on, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she just has to try it on, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Isn't this one lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Kouki and I are going to go for a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It really suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute, Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes like summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trivia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know animals are in miso soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:22:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Rin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,During Obon, when we went to visit grandpa's grave, the cicadas made a lot of noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There's a bellflower by the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When Daikichi saw that he started running.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "Precious to Grandpa"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is wa...kame! {here is a pun, because wakame is a kind of seaweed and kame is turtle}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:21.37,Note,,0,0,0,,Note: Wakame = Seaweed, Kame = Turtle
